There’s something to be said about an apartment that feels like home, and a community that feels like a neighborhood.
Just 2.5 miles from Crocker Park, Westchester Townhomes offers a place of peace: rental homes where smiling faces are the norm, and furry friends are considered family.
You’ll find our residents sauntering with their pups around these manicured grounds, or strolling around Downtown Bay Village.
Here, shop owners remember your name; quaint storefronts invite you in.
A little to the north, boats glide across the lake in the same, unhurried manner.
Come and see why so many delight in our community.
We can’t wait to meet and show you your new home.
